snippet.title: KINGDOM HEARTS HD 1.5 ReMIX PAX East Trailer (US)
snippet.description:
For the first time, KINGDOM HEARTS is available on PS3!

Follow Mickey, Goofy and Donald and relive the origins of the first three KINGDOM HEARTS games in gorgeous HD, with full PS3 trophy support, and all-new content.

-     KINGDOM HEARTS FINAL MIX

-     KINGDOM HEARTS Re:Chain of Memories

-     KINGDOM HEARTS 358/2 Days (HD cinematics)

Available this Fall exclusively on the PlayStation®3.

For more information about KINGDOM HEARTS HD 1.5 ReMIX, please visit www.kingdomhearts.com.

Like KINGDOM HEARTS at www.facebook.com/kingdomhearts 

Follow KINGDOM HEARTS at www.twitter.com/kingdomhearts
